{"tid":1634063,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"紅裝飾2.0 - 愛國陳百牆","createTime":"2019-10-07T06:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:57:16.000Z","uid":121409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2050dbe37c80436cb0910205c46e5d03bc765f7e","tid":1634063,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:24:25.000Z","msg":"前日開左個post想呼籲大家一齊送旗仔俾跣親嘅舖頭<br />\n<br />\n近排行街成日見到啲舖頭跣親，想送啲旗仔慰問佢地，你講我畫<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1626221\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1626221</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點知好似好多有心人都想慰問佢哋，畫到手都軟，真係捉晒蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我諗不如好似連儂牆咁，準備啲紙仔俾大家寫完貼上去，幫愛國商人表達下愛國訴求<br />\n紙仔嚟講，應該冇嘢比国旗更能表達愛國之情<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係好可惜塗污国旗係會俾差人叔叔拉返警署打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有自己畫啲差唔多嘅旗仔，大家都是紅旗，不用分那麼細，歡迎大家自己加字喺上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/twQXYy7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtwQXYy7.png&h=efcd522e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/18y29FP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F18y29FP.png&h=e62d4e47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GsrsBkU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsrsBkU.png&h=fd67ef62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p6JR20X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp6JR20X.png&h=5ba27ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎熱心嘅市民幫手表達老闆嘅心聲，就好似咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3u2qe0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3u2qe0.png&h=dfcc37c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/shDOkOw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FshDOkOw.png&h=12b1e915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都知有啲舖頭嘅老闆為愛國做左唔少事，大家都可以詳細寫出嚟表揚下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其是有啲連鎖店，有好多扮係高檔餐廳嘅舖頭，雖然紅色旗仔同佢哋高檔路線好似唔係好夾，但為左愛國，犧牲少少品味又算得啲咩，係咪咁講先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca424e37bddd7447f7144fc1105be04f987ca06","tid":1634063,"uid":121409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}